              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/44298927/" class="">第152页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/suliying/" class=" " title="大蘇老湿">大蘇老湿</a>
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="44298927">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">前面有几个小错没纠，这个谬误太明显了：“1931年，赫普沃斯用石膏创作了一件抽象艺术雕塑—后来毁于第一次世界大战—名叫《穿孔之形》（1931）。” 1931年才创作出来的，能毁于一战？EXM？？不知道是原著的谬误还是翻译的问题。 查询Barbara Hepworth的官网：里面是这样写的：“Hepworth's first holed sculpture, Pierced Form, probably carved in 1932, is exhibited there with the title Abstraction (it was subsequentl...</span>
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/44298927/">(<span class="">2回应</span>)</a>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2017-05-25 14:39</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <p>前面有几个小错没纠，这个谬误太明显了：“1931年，赫普沃斯用石膏创作了一件抽象艺术雕塑—后来毁于第一次世界大战—名叫《穿孔之形》（1931）。”</p><p>1931年才创作出来的，能毁于一战？EXM？？不知道是原著的谬误还是翻译的问题。</p><p>查询Barbara Hepworth的官网：里面是这样写的：“Hepworth's first holed sculpture, Pierced Form, probably carved in 1932, is exhibited there with the title Abstraction (it was subsequently destroyed in the war).” （source:<a href="http://barbarahepworth.org.uk/biography/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">http://barbarahepworth.org.uk/biography/</a>)</p><p>没说是哪场战争，不过用“subsequently destroyed in the war”，the指代的应该是二战吧。而且官网是用“probably carved in 1932”，也不是1931。</p>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
